CodeParser.parse_functions -> CodeParser.expr: exec(f'import {module} as {alias if alias else module}', eval_env)

CodeParser.construct_eval_env -> exec.expr: exec(f'import {module} as {alias if alias else module}', eval_env)

CodeParser.parse_callable_details -> Cod.expr: exec(f'import {module} as {alias if alias else module}', eval_env)

CodeParser.parse_function_def -> CodePar.expr: exec(f'import {module} as {alias if alias else module}', eval_env)

CodeParser.parse_classes -> CodeParser.p.expr: exec(f'import {module} as {alias if alias else module}', eval_env)

SFTBackend.create_job -> post.expr: requests.post(f'{host}{url}',                            json={'uri': uri, 'job_id': job_id, 'options': cls.CMD_OPTIONS, 'params': params})

SFTBackend.change_model_name -> post.expr: requests.post(f'{host}{url}',                            json={'uri': uri, 'job_id': job_id, 'old_model_name': old_model_name,                                  'model_name': model_name})

CodeInterpreterTool._run -> execute_code.expr: executor.submit(                subprocess.run,                cmd,                cwd=work_dir,                capture_output=True,                text=True,            )

execute_code -> submit.expr: executor.submit(                subprocess.run,                cmd,                cwd=work_dir,                capture_output=True,                text=True,            )

execute_function -> exec.expr: exec(                        f"{alias.asname or alias.name} = importlib.import_module('{alias.name}')",                        exec_globals,                        locals(),                    )
